sudo -u postgres psql postgres

postgres=# CREATE USER dev CREATEDB;
postgres=> \password dev
Enter new password: 
Enter it again: 
postgres=# \q

dev is your Linux/Vagarant username

Change the username/password in ./Rakefile and ./config/database.rb accordingly

